<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-1a' );" name="013-1a" class="pb">[013-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　詩總聞卷十三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:218'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　王質　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='218:224'>　　谷風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='224:231'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:254'>習習谷風維風及雨将恐将懼維予與汝将安将樂女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='254:259'>轉棄予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='259:279'>　此必同經患難而他時稍達棄恩忘舊者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='279:305'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-1b' );" name="013-1b" class="pb">[013-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='305:312'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='312:335'>習習谷風維風及頽将恐将懼寘予于懐将安将樂棄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='335:340'>予如遺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='340:351'>　頽雨圯山也亦雨也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='351:358'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='358:381'>習習谷風維山崔嵬無草不死無木不萎忘我大徳思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='381:386'>我小怨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='386:396'>　草木長則山愈髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='396:422'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-2a' );" name="013-2a" class="pb">[013-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='422:445'>　　聞音曰女忍與切予演女切懐胡隈切怨讀作徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='445:468'>　　　西北人相怨恨之聲此字以聲取旁紐作越亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='468:476'>　　　可叶徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='476:499'>總聞曰谷風春風也正草木發舒之時當是其人得時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='499:522'>逞志如草之繁如木之茂有莫已若之意恨者以為無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='522:545'>不死之草無不萎之木言無不卒之人人生幾何而惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='545:554'>薄如此恨之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='554:560'>　　蓼莪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='560:586'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-2b' );" name="013-2b" class="pb">[013-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='586:593'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='593:611'>蓼蓼者莪匪莪伊蒿哀哀父母生我劬勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='611:618'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='618:636'>蓼蓼者莪匪莪伊蔚哀哀父母生我勞悴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='636:659'>　非莪即蒿非莪即蔚目前唯有此物更無他見父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='659:682'>　生我本欲増光門户今乃索居田野如此嘆惋之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='682:686'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='686:693'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='693:719'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-3a' );" name="013-3a" class="pb">[013-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='719:740'>　缾之罄矣維罍之恥鮮民之生不如死之久矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='740:763'>　缾既罄罍又恥言窮甚鮮民之生言匱于生也既無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='763:784'>　一為生不如死也乆言當死已久至此已過也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='784:791'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='791:809'>無父何怙無母何恃出則銜恤入則靡至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='809:832'>　當是父母鍾愛有託不如所願而亡出門則銜憂口</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='832:855'>　如不能出聲也入門則無所至身又如不在家也大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='855:878'>　率口有所銜則聲不發神有所亂則目不識憂思之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='878:904'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-3b' );" name="013-3b" class="pb">[013-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='904:909'>　極也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='909:916'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='916:939'>父兮生我母兮鞠我拊我畜我長我育我顧我復我出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='939:952'>入腹我欲報之徳昊天罔極</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='952:962'>　欲報而不能報也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='962:969'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='969:992'>南山烈烈飄風發發民莫不穀我獨何害南山律律飄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='992:1005'>風弗弗民莫不穀我獨不卒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1005:1031'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-4a' );" name="013-4a" class="pb">[013-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1031:1054'>　人莫不有穀為食何我獨乏當是父母亦以傷貧遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1054:1070'>　至棄背故此人之辭若不可存者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1070:1085'>　　聞音曰蔚紆胃切害何葛切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1085:1106'>　　聞跡曰兩章皆稱南山故知居南山之下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1106:1129'>總聞曰毛氏父母病亡在役不得見尋詩不見此意當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1129:1152'>是不遇之窮士居南山之下遇苦寒之辰銜哀抱貧人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1152:1164'>不能堪則欲死葢常情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1164:1170'>　　大東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1170:1196'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-4b' );" name="013-4b" class="pb">[013-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1196:1203'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1203:1213'>有饛簋飱有捄棘匕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1213:1236'>　大東小東具見此詩無别有小東也簋列飱者也匕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1236:1259'>　取飱者也當是士大夫㑹集之間有見道路平直貴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1259:1277'>　賤徃來動念興哀思徃日而傷今日也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1277:1300'>周道如砥其直如矢君子所履小人所視睠言顧之澘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1300:1305'>焉出涕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1305:1312'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1312:1338'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-5a' );" name="013-5a" class="pb">[013-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1338:1348'>小東大東杼柚其空</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1348:1371'>　當是周道之側有大東山小東山俱在東而以大小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1371:1377'>　别之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1377:1400'>糾糾葛屨可以履霜佻佻公子行彼周行既徃既來使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1400:1405'>我心疚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1405:1428'>　葛屨公子行周行之屨也公子如此下民可知安得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1428:1434'>　不傷心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1434:1441'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1441:1467'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-5b' );" name="013-5b" class="pb">[013-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1467:1485'>有冽氿泉無浸穫薪契契寤嘆哀我憚人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1485:1508'>　此遇寒涉水而載薪者也以為氿泉勿浸我薪濕則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1508:1521'>　不可爇也此亦謂公子也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1521:1539'>薪是穫薪尚可載也哀我憚人亦可息也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1539:1562'>　薪雖濕尚可用也小人以勞致病則恐不可生願生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1562:1578'>　息也皆公子之徒愬貧勞之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1578:1585'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1585:1608'>東人之子職勞不來西人之子粲粲衣服舟人之子熊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1608:1634'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-6a' );" name="013-6a" class="pb">[013-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1634:1644'>小東大東杼柚其空</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1644:1667'>　當是周道之側有大東山小東山俱在東而以大小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1667:1673'>　别之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1673:1696'>糾糾葛屨可以履霜佻佻公子行彼周行既徃既來使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1696:1701'>我心疚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1701:1724'>　葛屨公子行周行之屨也公子如此下民可知安得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1724:1730'>　不傷心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1730:1737'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1737:1763'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-6b' );" name="013-6b" class="pb">[013-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='1763:1781'>有冽氿泉無浸穫薪契契寤嘆哀我憚人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='1781:1804'>　此遇寒涉水而載薪者也以為氿泉勿浸我薪濕則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='1804:1817'>　不可爇也此亦謂公子也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='1817:1835'>薪是穫薪尚可載也哀我憚人亦可息也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='1835:1858'>　薪雖濕尚可用也小人以勞致病則恐不可生願生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='1858:1874'>　息也皆公子之徒愬貧勞之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='1874:1881'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='1881:1904'>東人之子職勞不來西人之子粲粲衣服舟人之子熊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='1904:1930'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-7a' );" name="013-7a" class="pb">[013-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='1930:1943'>羆是裘私人之子百僚是試</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='1943:1966'>　此詩當是傷怨王室之詩是時周已遷東而秦踞西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='1966:1989'>　在東者憚所職之勞不肯来服王事在西者又逞勢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='1989:2012'>　得志而蔑視在東者也舟人水工之人私人家僮之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2012:2020'>　人皆西人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2020:2038'>或以其酒不以其漿鞙鞙佩璲不以其長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2038:2061'>　言舟人私人之徒皆酣于酒而不用漿務淳美也皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2061:2084'>　華其佩而不用長務輕捷也言西人得意如此而東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2084:2110'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-7b' );" name="013-7b" class="pb">[013-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2110:2126'>　人徒勞而甚窮嘆其不如西人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2126:2133'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2133:2156'>維天有漢監亦有光跂彼織女終日七㐮雖則七㐮不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2156:2161'>成報章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2161:2184'>　皆服勞之極逮夜及曉不休據所見道所懐自此而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2184:2206'>　下天漢織女牽牛啓明長庚捄畢南箕北斗是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2206:2213'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2213:2236'>睆彼牽牛不以服箱東有啓明西有長庚有捄天畢載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2236:2262'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-8a' );" name="013-8a" class="pb">[013-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2262:2267'>施之行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2267:2274'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2274:2297'>維南有箕不可以簸揚維北有斗不可以挹酒漿維南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2297:2313'>有箕載翕其舌維北有斗西柄之揭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2313:2336'>　宋氏所謂心悚惕而震盪何所憂之多方仰明月而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2336:2352'>　太息步列星而極明指星起興也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2352:2375'>　　聞音曰行户郎切來六直切疚訖力切載節力切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2375:2398'>　　　服蒲北切裘渠之切試申之切旁紐則然易可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2398:2424'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-8b' );" name="013-8b" class="pb">[013-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2424:2447'>　　　貞無咎固有之也無妄之藥不可試也庚古郎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2447:2457'>　　　切揭居竭切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2457:2480'>總聞曰有指君不明者天漢是也有指臣無用者織女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2480:2503'>牽牛啓明長庚畢箕斗是也東西南北無不周覧興懐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2503:2525'>大率首章睠言顧之澘焉出涕此其真情之大端也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2525:2531'>　　四月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2531:2538'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2538:2548'>四月維夏六月徂暑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2548:2574'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-9a' );" name="013-9a" class="pb">[013-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2574:2597'>　當是初夏出征厯秋厯冬又次年厯春厯秋在道凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2597:2608'>　經年有餘尋詩可見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2608:2618'>先祖匪人胡寜忍予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2618:2641'>　我先祖獨非人而何為忍于我也此必其祖在位有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2641:2656'>　勞而其後為有力者所不容也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2656:2663'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2663:2681'>秋日凄凄百卉具腓亂離瘼矣奚其適歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2681:2691'>　日色惨七月侯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2691:2717'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-9b' );" name="013-9b" class="pb">[013-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='2717:2724'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='2724:2742'>冬日烈烈飄風發發民莫不穀我獨何害</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='2742:2752'>　日色寒十月候也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='2752:2759'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='2759:2777'>山有嘉卉侯栗侯梅廢為殘賊莫知其尤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='2777:2797'>　此登山有見也栗熟八月後梅熟五月後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='2797:2804'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='2804:2822'>相彼泉水載清載濁我日構禍曷云能穀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='2822:2849'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-10a' );" name="013-10a" class="pb">[013-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='2849:2872'>　此臨水所見也泉水彼清而復濁雨多泉溢也水生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='2872:2879'>　三月後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='2879:2886'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='2886:2904'>滔滔江漢南國之紀盡瘁以仕寜莫我有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='2904:2915'>　此從事江漢之間也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='2915:2922'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='2922:2940'>匪鶉匪鳶翰飛戾天匪鱣匪鮪潜逃于淵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='2940:2963'>　此仰觀飛俯視潜有見者也我非羽焉能飛我非鱗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='2963:2990'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-10b' );" name="013-10b" class="pb">[013-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='2990:3002'>　焉能潜言無所避害也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3002:3009'>　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3009:3027'>山有蕨薇隰有杞桋君子作歌維以告哀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3027:3050'>　草木生三月後也大率年餘在外道塗江山之間可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3050:3074'>　謂盡瘁而不知有我視若無人可謂太無情是可哀也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3074:3097'>　　聞音曰予演女切害何葛切尤于其切濁厨玉切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3097:3110'>　　　有羽軌切哀於希切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3110:3128'>總聞曰自謂為君子所以自别于小人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3128:3155'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-11a' );" name="013-11a" class="pb">[013-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3155:3161'>　　北山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3161:3168'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3168:3178'>陟彼北山言采其杞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3178:3193'>　杞枸杞也仲春可食當是此時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3193:3211'>偕偕士子朝夕從事王事靡盬憂我父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3211:3218'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3218:3241'>溥天之下莫非王土率土之濱莫非王臣大夫不均我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3241:3247'>從事獨賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3247:3274'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-11b' );" name="013-11b" class="pb">[013-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3274:3296'>　賢如某賢于某若干純之賢言其勞獨過于人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3296:3303'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3303:3326'>四牡彭彭王事傍傍嘉我未老鮮我方將旅力方剛經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3326:3331'>營四方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3331:3353'>　以我少壯而使我陳力固當然但不均為可恨耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3353:3360'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3360:3383'>或燕燕居息或盡瘁事國或息偃在牀或不已于行或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3383:3394'>不知呌號或慘慘劬勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3394:3421'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-12a' );" name="013-12a" class="pb">[013-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3421:3428'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3428:3451'>或棲遲偃仰或王事鞅掌或湛樂飲酒或慘慘畏咎或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3451:3462'>出入風議或靡事不為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3462:3471'>　此所謂不均也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3471:3494'>　　聞音曰事上止切下後五切賢下珍切今東人猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='3494:3517'>　　　有此音彭鋪郎切國越逼切行户郎切議魚羈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='3517:3540'>　　　切今西人猶有此音佛書思議讀作冝大率西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='3540:3548'>　　　音多然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='3548:3575'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-12b' );" name="013-12b" class="pb">[013-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='3575:3597'>　　聞訓曰嘉鮮皆美之辭今人猶呼少壯為鮮徤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='3597:3620'>總聞曰不均歸咎于大夫大夫以君命而役庶位者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='3620:3630'>大率詩人于君多婉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='3630:3638'>　　無將大車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='3638:3645'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='3645:3655'>無將大車祗自塵兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='3655:3678'>　不必將大車當時大車皆小人乗之我乗大車亦與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='3678:3690'>　小人同倫但自汚而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='3690:3717'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-13a' );" name="013-13a" class="pb">[013-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='3717:3727'>無思百憂祗自疷兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='3727:3734'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='3734:3752'>無將大車維塵㝠㝠無思百憂不出于熲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='3752:3777'>　言憂思無精采也今人猶呼物陳弊為少出治治讀作持</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='3777:3784'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='3784:3802'>無將大車維塵雍兮無思百憂祗自重兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='3802:3832'>　　聞音曰疷眉貧切疷當通作□集韻與<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2188' title='KR2188' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2188.png'/>同皆病</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='3832:3856'>　　　也吳氏以字書民氐多互用盖經唐諱從民皆改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='3856:3883'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-13b' );" name="013-13b" class="pb">[013-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='3883:3907'>　　　從氏後有復者有不復者且如緡緍一也而有兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='3907:3931'>　　　從錉鍲一也亦有兩從秦諱改正月遂以灰為平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='3931:3955'>　　　至今不改况唐三百年又重之以五代之唐江南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='3955:3977'>　　　之唐習熟不全改易爾㝠莫逈切重直龍切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='3977:3993'>　　聞訓曰雍壅也北人猶作此音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='3993:4016'>總聞曰賢者不願居髙位居髙位則任重事世態若此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4016:4039'>髙位不可居重事不可任莫若自顧為安三章連稱三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4039:4055'>自自者已也使人懐此心安得不亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4055:4082'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-14a' );" name="013-14a" class="pb">[013-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4082:4088'>　　小明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4088:4095'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4095:4118'>明明上天照臨下土我征徂西至于艽野二月初吉載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4118:4131'>離寒暑心之憂矣其毒太苦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4131:4154'>　徂西徃舊都也此必有求于秦而識者知秦之心無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4154:4177'>　厭是豈可倚如被毒而又至苦言毒之深也艽説文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4177:4193'>　逺荒也引此至于艽野一曰獸蓐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4193:4203'>念彼共人涕零如雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4203:4230'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-14b' );" name="013-14b" class="pb">[013-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4230:4253'>　共人在朝之相知也不堪在外之惡境故思在朝之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4253:4276'>　相知至于淚滂流首重回又甚于夜卧起宿于外不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4276:4288'>　能宿于内也念之極也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4288:4298'>豈不懐歸畏此罪罟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4298:4321'>　固知其無成而思歸必以為我為懐私不辦事也置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4321:4345'>　我于罪罟加我以譴怒甚至于使我再行尤不可堪也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4345:4352'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4352:4375'>昔我往矣日月方除曷云其還嵗聿云莫念我獨兮我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4375:4402'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-15a' );" name="013-15a" class="pb">[013-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4402:4425'>事孔庶心之憂矣憚我不暇念彼共人睠睠懐顧豈不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4425:4433'>懐歸畏此譴怒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4433:4449'>　除開也言天氣方開明也二月後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4449:4456'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4456:4479'>昔我往矣日月方奥曷云其還政事愈蹙嵗聿云莫采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4479:4502'>蕭穫菽心之憂矣自貽伊戚念彼共人興言出宿豈不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4502:4510'>懐歸畏此反覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='4510:4533'>　奥煖也言天氣方暄煖也四月後二章嵗聿云莫亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='4533:4560'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-15b' );" name="013-15b" class="pb">[013-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='4560:4570'>　參差古作欲語健</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='4570:4577'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='4577:4600'>嗟爾君子無恒安處靖共爾位正直是與神之聽之式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='4600:4605'>穀以女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='4605:4612'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='4612:4635'>嗟爾君子無恒安息靖共爾位好是正直神之聽之介</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='4635:4640'>爾景福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='4640:4663'>　前三章此念彼共人故稱我稱彼後二章彼嗟爾君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='4663:4690'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-16a' );" name="013-16a" class="pb">[013-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='4690:4713'>　子故稱爾稱女以為進則嬰外藩之釁退則詒内朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='4713:4736'>　之譴進退故不能逃禍但不以偷安為念而以靖共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='4736:4756'>　正直為懐神必相扶而可免患相寛之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='4756:4779'>　　聞音曰野上與切除直慮切莫幕故切暇胡故切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='4779:4792'>　　　戚子六切福筆力切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='4792:4815'>總聞曰自二月初吉至嵗聿云暮所厯期年是時平王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='4815:4838'>以陕西予秦以河内予晉既以謝二國之援且以資二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='4838:4861'>國之助自秦仲已張至是立西畤泰畤密畤漸進汧渭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='4861:4888'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-16b' );" name="013-16b" class="pb">[013-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='4888:4911'>之間盡包關輔之地故以王命使西土者皆恐蹈不測</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='4911:4934'>也秦以虎狼處已以魚肉視人其來已久著于孝公成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='4934:4948'>于始皇當時有識者必先覺之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='4948:4954'>　　鼓鐘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='4954:4961'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='4961:4983'>鼓鐘将将淮水湯湯憂心且傷淑人君子懐允不忘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='4983:4990'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='4990:5012'>鼔鐘喈喈淮水湝湝憂心且悲淑人君子其徳不回</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5012:5039'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-17a' );" name="013-17a" class="pb">[013-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5039:5046'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5046:5068'>鼓鐘伐鼛淮有三洲憂心且妯淑人君子其徳不猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5068:5091'>　大率淮夷叛服不常當是前此既服至此又騷将帥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5091:5114'>　經理者合樂臨戎以此夸耀下國而懾服夷心識者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5114:5137'>　憂其不可故以美辭曉将帥爾懐至信彼且感服其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5137:5160'>　次以正以斷此事不患難辦回曲也猶疑也古稱猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5160:5183'>　豫猶多疑之獸也語曰猶之與人也出納之吝謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5183:5206'>　有司言有司出納遲疑吝惜如猶之状故謂之惡今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5206:5233'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-17b' );" name="013-17b" class="pb">[013-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5233:5240'>　併載于此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5240:5247'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5247:5269'>鼓鐘欽欽鼔瑟鼔琴笙磬同音以雅以南以籥不僣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5269:5292'>　鼓鐘瑟琴笙磬籥凡七器雅南凡二音諸器皆用二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5292:5315'>　音儀禮歌者關雎鹿鳴等今存笙者南陔由儀管者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5315:5338'>　新宫等今亡歌有辭今伊州渭州之類是也笙歌無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5338:5361'>　辭有腔今四六句合之類是也有辭者多存有腔無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5361:5374'>　辭者多亡葢無辭故難傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5374:5401'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-18a' );" name="013-18a" class="pb">[013-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5401:5424'>　　聞音曰将七羊切湯戸羊切喈居奚切湝弦雞切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5424:5441'>　　　鼛居尤切南尼心切僣七心切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5441:5453'>　　聞跡曰三洲在山陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5453:5476'>總聞曰漢以亡為無無其辭但有其題也以題推之其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5476:5499'>義略可見如此則可所謂惟存其義而逸其辭恐無是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5499:5522'>理也識者更詳今甲子旬中無戌亥甲戌旬中無申酉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5522:5545'>之類謂之空亡亡亦無也非漢字猶爾古語多然至後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5545:5568'>誤呼之元祐間善政綱舉而綱踈首選劉棠大統一王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5568:5595'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-18b' );" name="013-18b" class="pb">[013-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5595:5618'>勞心四方法三尺以雖具獄一人而使亡用西漢天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='5618:5641'>亡一人之獄棠天下名儒猶誤呼以為常誤呼可也而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='5641:5661'>義亦隨變則有所不可此類甚多今併載于此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='5661:5667'>　　楚茨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='5667:5674'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='5674:5692'>楚楚者茨言抽其棘自昔何為我蓻黍稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='5692:5715'>　抽拔也除也拔除茨棘而蓻黍稷自昔者謂后稷也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='5715:5738'>　下詩言自古亦謂后稷大凡詩人言祭祀必以農事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='5738:5765'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-19a' );" name="013-19a" class="pb">[013-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='5765:5788'>　起辭言農事必以祭祀續辭言農事祭祀必以福禄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='5788:5801'>　結辭三者未有闕一者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='5801:5824'>我黍與與我稷翼翼我倉既盈我庾維億以為酒食以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='5824:5837'>享以祀以妥以侑以介景福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='5837:5851'>　此總言享祀妥侑而助福也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='5851:5858'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='5858:5881'>濟濟蹌蹌絜爾牛羊以徃蒸嘗或剥或亨或肆或将祀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='5881:5903'>祭于祊祀事孔明先祖是皇神保是饗孝孫有慶報</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='5903:5930'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-19b' );" name="013-19b" class="pb">[013-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='5930:5939'>以介福萬壽無疆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='5939:5962'>　此總言牲牢既具先使祝致祭于門然後延尸入坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='5962:5974'>　也禮設祭于堂祊于外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='5974:5981'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='5981:6004'>執爨踖踖為俎孔碩或燔或炙君婦莫莫為豆孔庶為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6004:6027'>賓為客獻醻交錯禮儀卒度笑語卒獲神保是格報以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6027:6035'>介福萬壽攸酢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6035:6058'>　此次言俎豆各獻而祖尸為主餘昭穆為賓客亦皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6058:6085'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-20a' );" name="013-20a" class="pb">[013-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6085:6108'>　有尸大率禮皆以生代死貴通情也所謂事死如事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6108:6117'>　生事亡如事存</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='6117:6124'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='6124:6147'>我孔熯矣式禮莫愆工祝致告徂賚孝孫苾芬孝祀神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='6147:6170'>嗜飲食卜爾百福如幾如式既齊既稷既匡既勅永錫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='6170:6178'>爾極時萬時億</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='6178:6201'>　此次言俎豆甚乾飲食畢盡也進飲進食中禮無愆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='6201:6224'>　也工祝致神意以告孝孫初一章止言福之大而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='6224:6251'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-20b' );" name="013-20b" class="pb">[013-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='6251:6274'>　言福之數二章三章言萬至此自百至萬至萬自億</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='6274:6284'>　徂賚于是為多也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='6284:6291'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='6291:6314'>禮儀既備鐘鼓既戒孝孫徂位工祝致告神具醉止皇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='6314:6335'>尸載起鼓鐘送尸神保聿歸諸宰君婦廢徹不遲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='6335:6358'>　孝孫始離位而立庭既受賚則徃歸位也工祝以畢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='6358:6381'>　告尸乃起而歸宰廢主婦徹器各随其職而既其事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='6381:6404'>　也不遲者纔送尸即享福受胙也禮君親牽牲大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='6404:6431'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-21a' );" name="013-21a" class="pb">[013-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='6431:6454'>　贊幣而從君親制祭夫人薦盎君親割牲夫人薦酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='6454:6474'>　卿大夫從君命婦從夫人宰卿大夫以下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='6474:6484'>諸父兄弟備言燕私</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='6484:6507'>　諸宰君婦亟疾廢徹以享神之物及致祭之人所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='6507:6530'>　飲福受胙也尊屬如諸父者皆與卑属如諸弟者皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='6530:6553'>　與中屬如諸兄者皆與三者總諸屬也所以言備言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='6553:6557'>　私</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='6557:6564'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='6564:6591'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-21b' );" name="013-21b" class="pb">[013-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='6591:6614'>樂具入奏以綏後禄爾殽既将莫怨具慶既醉既飽小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6614:6627'>大稽首神嗜飲食使君壽考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6627:6650'>　樂飲福之樂也不特暫安而仍有后禄殽受胙之殽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6650:6673'>　也不特無怨而又皆有慶所願如此也方在祭尸為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='6673:6696'>　主故稱孝孫及飲福君為主故稱君凡祭事祝嘏稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='6696:6719'>　主人曰孝孫主人自稱曰曽孫大率周禮皆宗后稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='6719:6728'>　故皆稱曽孫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='6728:6746'>孔惠孔時維其盡之子子孫孫勿替引之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='6746:6773'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-22a' );" name="013-22a" class="pb">[013-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='6773:6796'>　禮既順物又時享祀之道盡矣惟勿廢而長行之此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='6796:6811'>　皆美辭末有戒禮為大順次之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='6811:6834'>　　聞音曰祀逸織切福筆力切亨鋪郎切祊蒲光切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='6834:6857'>　　　明謨郎切享虚良切慶墟羊切踖七略切碩常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='6857:6880'>　　　約切炙陟略切莫末各切客克各切度徒洛切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='6880:6903'>　　　穫黄郭切格剛鶴切愆起巾切備蒲北切戒訖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='6903:6926'>　　　力切位力入切周官建國之神位故書位作力</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='6926:6949'>　　　鄭氏云立讀為位同字古文春秋公即位為公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='6949:6976'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-22b' );" name="013-22b" class="pb">[013-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='6976:6999'>　　　即立鄭氏以二字當同為位知其一未知其二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='6999:7022'>　　　也既可同為位亦可同為立左氏賦以日叶位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='7022:7045'>　　　江氏詩以位叶匹信古有此音也告古得切奏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='7045:7068'>　　　臧后切旁紐千木切叶禄慶墟羊切飽補掫切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='7068:7085'>　　　考去久切盡子忍切引一忍切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='7085:7108'>　　聞人曰神保尸之賛相也凡享凡酢凡歸皆賛相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='7108:7127'>　　　導之保氏掌祭祀之客恐亦是此職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='7127:7150'>總聞曰此詩本末甚詳禮祭稱孝孫孝子以其義稱曽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='7150:7177'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-23a' );" name="013-23a" class="pb">[013-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='7177:7200'>孫某謂國家也祝嘏稱其義故曰孝主人于國于家皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='7200:7223'>稱次故稱曽尸神象也祝將命也夏立尸而卒祭商坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='7223:7246'>尸周旅酧六尸三昭三穆與太祖而七后稷太祖也后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='7246:7269'>稷之尸發爵不受旅其旅者太祖以次也傳主人辭于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='7269:7292'>神曰祝傳尸辭于主人曰嘏其文載于經傳甚多亦不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='7292:7308'>無相牴牾擇其明簡者一二略載之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='7308:7315'>　　信南山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='7315:7322'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='7322:7349'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-23b' );" name="013-23b" class="pb">[013-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='7349:7367'>信彼南山維禹甸之畇畇原隰曽孫田之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='7367:7390'>　稱禹即是稱稷書先命禹作司空次命棄為后稷言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='7390:7403'>　水土稼穡相維皆為急也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='7403:7413'>我疆我理南東其畆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='7413:7436'>　古制畆法鄉南而帶東不言東南而言南東也平田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='7436:7459'>　四方皆一制葢疆理所經遂上之徑溝上之畛洫上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='7459:7482'>　之塗澮上之道川上之路以達于畿皆背畆而面畿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='7482:7505'>　畆在東南畿在西北古者正塗皆取定域非若今有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='7505:7532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-24a' );" name="013-24a" class="pb">[013-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='7532:7555'>　小路有義路也所謂欲使齊之封内盡東其畆惟吾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='7555:7578'>　子戎車是利無顧土冝葢晉嚮齊直東則順自南而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='7578:7588'>　東則逆亦引此事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='7588:7595'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='7595:7618'>上天同雲雨雪雰雰益之以霡霂既優既渥既霑既足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='7618:7624'>生我百穀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='7624:7647'>　麥欲雪先雪滋麥禾欲雨次雨滋穀故曰益之言得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='7647:7670'>　雪之後又加得之雨為佳雪當在冬雨當在春夏斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='7670:7697'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-24b' );" name="013-24b" class="pb">[013-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='7697:7703'>　為時也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='7703:7710'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='7710:7733'>疆場翼翼黍稷彧彧曽孫之穡以為酒食畀我尸賓壽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='7733:7738'>考萬年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='7738:7761'>　尸主又有尸賓皆代為神者也既畀尸主又畀尸賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='7761:7784'>　當是楚茨大祭尸主尸賓同享此小祭后稷不與而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='7784:7807'>　獨以次也大率大祭亦于后稷之尸以逺故加嚴所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='7807:7815'>　謂不受旅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='7815:7842'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-25a' );" name="013-25a" class="pb">[013-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='7842:7849'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='7849:7873'>中田有廬疆埸有𤓰是剥是菹獻之皇祖曽孫壽考受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='7873:7878'>天之祜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='7878:7902'>　𤓰熟而薦廟也當是夏時此薦新之祭差小故其禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='7902:7914'>　比楚茨蒸嘗之祭差簡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l445' data-llen='7914:7921'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l446' data-llen='7921:7944'>祭以清祭從以騂牡享于祖考執其鸞刀以啟其毛取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l447' data-llen='7944:7949'>其血膋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l448' data-llen='7949:7976'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-25b' );" name="013-25b" class="pb">[013-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l449' data-llen='7976:7999'>　雖薦新亦用牲但不用大牲禮薦氷以羔薦麥以彘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l450' data-llen='7999:8022'>　薦含桃以雛薦麻薦稻皆以犬惟薦鮪薦魚薦穀無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l451' data-llen='8022:8046'>　牲此薦𤓰之牲也商周鼎鹵多作子象持刀度當時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l452' data-llen='8046:8069'>　事神主人自執刀割牲舞自秉干戚籍田自秉耒之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l453' data-llen='8069:8081'>　類也騂色牡形他皆可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l454' data-llen='8081:8088'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l455' data-llen='8088:8111'>是烝是享苾苾芬芬祀事孔明先祖是皇報以介福萬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l456' data-llen='8111:8116'>壽無疆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l457' data-llen='8116:8143'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-26a' );" name="013-26a" class="pb">[013-26a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l458' data-llen='8143:8166'>　楚茨烝嘗之祭也其儀差詳信南山薦新之祭也其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l459' data-llen='8166:8189'>　儀差略下章再田社祭社以方也大田蜡祭蜡亦以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l460' data-llen='8189:8212'>　方也皇祖謂太王王季先祖謂文王考謂武王大率</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l461' data-llen='8212:8235'>　當祭止自太王以下謂之近廟故此皇祖有獻無享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l462' data-llen='8235:8239'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l463' data-llen='8239:8262'>　　聞音曰田堂練切今人亦呼作田為佃田呼農家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l464' data-llen='8262:8285'>　　　為佃戸皆作去音吴氏佃作池隣切田作池因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l465' data-llen='8285:8308'>　　　切又皆作享年切不若從本音為順畆滿罪切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l466' data-llen='8308:8335'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-26b' );" name="013-26b" class="pb">[013-26b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l467' data-llen='8335:8358'>　　　渥烏谷切易林春多膏澤下潤倸渥稼穡熟成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l468' data-llen='8358:8381'>　　　畆獲百斛正用此詩是知上天同雲至生我百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l469' data-llen='8381:8404'>　　　穀六句包春夏冬三時非止一時也或于逼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l470' data-llen='8404:8428'>　　　年禰因切𤓰攻乎切祜候古切考去久切享虚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l471' data-llen='8428:8439'>　　　良切明謨郎切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l472' data-llen='8439:8462'>　　聞跡曰大率田井之制一夫居一㕓田百畆此則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l473' data-llen='8462:8485'>　　　上中下地皆同上萊五十畆中萊一百畆下萊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l474' data-llen='8485:8508'>　　　二百畆謂不耕而陸種者也今一夫一户也餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l475' data-llen='8508:8535'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-27a' );" name="013-27a" class="pb">[013-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l476' data-llen='8535:8558'>　　　夫一户之衍出者也亦在一户受㕓受畆之内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l477' data-llen='8558:8581'>　　　猶今言子戸古之度量皆極短于今若如舊説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l478' data-llen='8581:8604'>　　　則地太寛人太少有所不足如今所計人力地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l479' data-llen='8604:8616'>　　　力皆相當無遺也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l480' data-llen='8616:8639'>總聞曰兩詩皆言祀事孔明所謂逮闇而祭日不足繼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l481' data-llen='8639:8662'>之以燭古以為非至室事交乎戸堂事交乎階質明而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l482' data-llen='8662:8681'>始行事晏朝而退古以為是孔明葢謂此也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l483' data-llen='8681:8684'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l484' data-llen='8684:8711'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '013-27b' );" name="013-27b" class="pb">[013-27b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
